extensionDescription.message: Facebook Container isola tu activitate de Facebook ab le resto de tu activitate pro impedir a Facebook de traciar te foras de su sito via le cookies de tertie partes.
extensionDescription.description: Description of the extension. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

in-fbc-subhead.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on a Facebook website, which has been automatically opened into Facebook Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

in-fbc-p1.message: Facebook pote ora traciar te sur iste sito. Pro remover iste sito ex Facebook Container, elige Sitos consentite in Facebook Container e remove lo del lista.

on-facebook-subhead.message: Sur Facebook e sitos in le dominio de Facebook Container
on-facebook-subhead.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on a Facebook website, which has been automatically opened into Facebook Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

on-facebook-p1.message: Iste icone appare in le barra de adresse de Firefox quando tu visita sitos gerite per Facebook o sitos que tu ha addite a Facebook Container.
on-facebook-p1.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop-up when the user is on a Facebook website, which has been automatically opened into Facebook Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

on-facebook-p2.message: Iste sitos besonia, pro functionar, de acceder a tu identitate de Facebook (o de saper qui es tu). Isto significa alsi que Facebook pote traciar toto lo que tu face sur iste sitos.
on-facebook-p2.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop up when the user is on Facebook.

notOnFacebookHeader.message: $URL$ non es in le Facebook Container.
notOnFacebookHeader.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is NOT on a Facebook website, which has been automatically opened OUTSIDE Facebook Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

notOnFacebookText.message: Iste sito es foras de Facebook Container. Isto rende plus difficile a Facebook traciar te tra le Web.
notOnFacebookText.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop-up when the user is NOT on a Facebook website, which has been automatically opened OUTSIDE Facebook Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

onUnknownSiteHeader.message: Iste sito non es in le Facebook Container.
onUnknownSiteHeader.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on an "unknown" website - e.g., about:newtab. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

facebookContainer.description: This is the name of the extension, and appears at the top of all onboarding panels. Please do not translate "Facebook Container".

onboarding1-subhead.description: This is the subhead of onboarding panel 1. Please do not translate "Facebook Container"

onboarding1-p1.message: Facebook pote traciar tu exploration ben ultra Facebook.com. Facebook Como e Compartir Le buttones Me place e Compartir, per exemplo, pote traciar ubi tu ha essite — mesmo sur paginas que tu jammais ha marcate como Me place o que tu ha compartite.
onboarding1-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of onboarding panel 1. Please do not translate "Facebook Container"

onboarding1-p2.message: Facebook Container crea un limite inter le sitos Facebook e le resto del web, assi il es plus difficile pro Facebook traciar te online.

onboarding2-subhead.message: Sur Facebook e sitos in le dominio de Facebook Container
onboarding2-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the second onboarding panel. Please do not translate "Facebook Container"

onboarding2-alt.message: Le icone barriera de Facebook Container
onboarding2-alt.description: This is alternative text for the icon in the second onboarding panel

onboarding2-p1.message: Iste icone appare in le barra de adresse de Firefox quando tu visita sitos, como Facebook.com, que es gerite per Facebook Container.
onboarding2-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the second onboarding panel.

onboarding2-p2.message: Iste sitos besonia, pro functionar, de acceder a tu identitate de Facebook (o de saper qui es tu). Isto significa alsi que Facebook pote traciar toto lo que tu face sur iste sitos.
onboarding2-p2.description: This is the second paragraph of the second onboarding panel. Please do not translate "Facebook Container"

onboarding3-subhead.message: Como sape io si Facebook Container functiona?
onboarding3-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the third onboarding panel.

onboarding3-p1.message: Le buttones que te consenti de marcar Me place o Compartir cosas in Facebook, o que te lassa acceder a sitos web per tu conto Facebook, contine traciatores. Facebook Container blocara iste traciatores e monstra le icone barriera pro te monstrar ubi le traciatores era eliminate.
onboarding3-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the third onboarding panel.

onboarding3-img.message: Iste imagine demonstra como le icone barriera de Facebook Container parera in le pagina a latere del button Me place de Facebook.
onboarding3-img.description: This is alternative text for the image shown in the third onboarding panel.

onboarding3-p2.message: Comocunque, si tu clicca sur ulle de iste buttones Facebook potera te traciar.
onboarding3-p2.description: This is the second paragraph on the third onboarding panel.

btn-allow.description: This is a button to allows users to whitelist the domain, adding it to the Facebook container.

btn-cancel.description: This is a button to cancel out of the onboarding panel.

btn-next.description: This is a button to continue to the next onboarding panel.

btn-back.description: This is a button that returns the user to the previous onboarding panel.

btn-done.description: This is a button the user clicks to close out the panel when they have finished reading the text.

btn-arrow-back.description: This is alternative text for the back arrow button.

btn-arrow-forward.message: Ir a Como functiona Facebook Container
btn-arrow-forward.description: This is alternative text for the arrow icon next to the "How Facebook Container Works" link

no-trackers-p1.message: Facebook Container non ha detegite traciatores de Facebook sur iste pagina. Nonobstante, le pagina poterea continer altere typos de traciatores.

learn-more.description: This is a link that opens a page with more information about Facebook Container.

how-fbc-works.description: This is a button that opens the Facebook Container onboarding flow.

trackers-detected-subhead.message: Nos te ha protegite de Facebook.
trackers-detected-subhead.description: This is a subhead, and it means that the add on has protected the user by blocking Facebook trackers.

trackers-detected-p1.message: Le buttones de Facebook que pare sur compras, novas e altere sitos contine traciatores que conta a Facebook ubi tu ha essite sur le web. Mesmo si tu jammais usa iste buttones pro marcar Me place o Compartir, le traciatores pote ancora colliger datos re tu exploration. Facebook Container bloca iste traciatores.

trackers-detected-p2.message: Facebook Container bloca iste traciatores. Comocunque, si tu clicca sur ulle de iste buttones Facebook potera te traciar.

trackers-detected-fence-alt.message: Barriera de Facebook Container con escudo.
trackers-detected-fence-alt.description: This is alternative text describing the container fence icon.

sites-included.description: This is a header for the list of websites that are in the Facebook Container by default. Capitalized letters are preferred if that makes sense/is feasible for the language.

no-sites-added.description: This message is shown beneath the 'SITES YOU’VE ALLOWED' list header when no sites have been added to the contaner.

sites-allowed.description: This is the header for the list of sites the user has manually added into the Facebook Container. Capitalized letters are preferred if that makes sense/is feasible for the lanaguage.

sites-added-p1.message: Facebook Container pone sitos gerite per Facebook intra le limite. Tu pote consentir altere sitos in le limite, ma isto consentira a Facebook de traciar plus de tu exploration web.

remove-site-p1.message: Le remotion de iste sito ab Facebook Container significa que le accesso con functionalitate Facebook non functionara plus e le cookies de traciamento de Facebook sera delite.

remove-site-p2.message: Si tu vole usar de novo le accesso per Facebook, tu debera lo re-adder a Facebook Container.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-share.message: Facebook Container ha disactivate iste button e blocate Facebook de traciar tu visita a iste pagina.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-login.message: Facebook Container ha blocate traciatores de Facebook. Si tu usa le accesso per Facebook sur iste sito, illo potera traciar te.

inPageUI-tooltip-prompt-p1.message: Consenti a Facebook de te traciar ci?

inPageUI-tooltip-prompt-p2.message: Si tu vole usar le accesso per Facebook, pois illo potera traciar tu activitate sur iste sito. Isto pote les adjutar a construer un imagine plus complete de tu vita online.

inPageUI-tooltip-prompt-checkbox.message: Non me lo monstrar de novo
